{"tid":260060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加揚言繼續豪獎牌畀人","createTime":"2017-05-27T12:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T18:40:28.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b42f9220f81fe56739dce0093810a2f606f6107","tid":260060,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JztM1fgw8aysWUEKtbiZ6r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2a7e4c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加表示，即使周六擊敗車路士贏得足總盃冠軍，他也不會選擇自己保留冠軍獎牌，會把它轉贈予一些從未贏得這面獎牌的人。<br />\n<br />\n若然阿仙奴周六在英足盃決賽擊敗車路士捧盃的話，那將會是兵工廠4年來的第3次稱王，亦會是阿仙奴領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）個人歷來第7次高舉足總盃，儘管足總盃對雲帥滿有意義，但他坦言即使奪冠也不會保留冠軍獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n雲加說：「我家裡是沒有任何錦標的獎牌，你到我家時將會感覺驚訝，沒有獎盃，沒有獎牌，甚麼都沒有，我全都轉贈別人，球會內總有人或員工是沒有獎牌的，因此，我轉贈給他們，總找到會接收它的人。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不是一個回望過去的人，我總向前展望，在家你甚至不會猜想到我是一個足球領隊，與事實不同，我不是要跟足球分隔，反之，我全程投入足球，我只會在比賽當天觀看比賽，但不會回望己隊從前勝出過甚麼，做到過甚麼，還有輸掉過甚麼。」"},{"pid":"b99addd76cc0c9d6075ff9aa70eb453e542f969f","tid":260060,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dba86fa728a6ea3381ccafdda9b26c92803491","tid":260060,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"送俾干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe2ca4de46660a5ca8ca19e708204dd70ab4035","tid":260060,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JztM1fgw8aysWUEKtbiZ6r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2a7e4c41\" target=\"_blank\">http://now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加表示，即使周六擊敗車路士贏得足總盃冠軍，他也不會選擇自己保留冠軍獎牌，會把它轉贈予一些從未贏得這面獎牌的人。<br />\n<br />\n若然阿仙奴周六在英足盃決賽擊敗車路士捧盃的話，那將會是兵工廠4年來的第3次稱王，亦會是阿仙奴領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）個人歷來第7次高舉足總盃，儘管足總盃對雲帥滿有意義，但他坦言即使奪冠也不會保留冠軍獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n雲加說：「我家裡是沒有任何錦標的獎牌，你到我家時將會感覺驚訝，沒有獎盃，沒有獎牌，甚麼都沒有，我全都轉贈別人，球會內總有人或員工是沒有獎牌的，因此，我轉贈給他們，總找到會接收它的人。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不是一個回望過去的人，我總向前展望，在家你甚至不會猜想到我是一個足球領隊，與事實不同，我不是要跟足球分隔，反之，我全程投入足球，我只會在比賽當天觀看比賽，<span style=\"color: red;\">但不會回望己隊從前勝出過甚麼，做到過甚麼，還有輸掉過甚麼。</span>」</blockquote><br />\n唔怪之得轉個陣要轉咁撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe91f67afffafb1c4253fb7602b1851c9da0bec","tid":260060,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送俾干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906e7ee277f0047126b7c55f4a8eca09c9c242aa","tid":260060,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492c8a14ca4bb2acefa74451ed38d7a8147cc465","tid":260060,"uid":435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送俾干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪送左個英超囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12184e869484d711254bf5192a88d26dcbb46212","tid":260060,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送俾干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪送左個英超囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger路?"},{"pid":"85b8e95108ac2cfefea145791f9ff18323cae4f7","tid":260060,"uid":34387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}